reviews.review_text: The Rainbow Makers Here they are.

Good ole 73’ I dont rate songs,I do rate shows. This is one of the standout performances of 1973. It has about every thing a DH could ask for. No details here from me,it would take toooolong.I cant believe there are not more views but it will get around.
Only thing better is to listen to this show again!!
